	dprr:hasNoteText "Prosecuted Camillus and forced him into exile (Liv. 5.32.8-9; Val. Max. 5.3.2a; Plut. Cam. 12-13; cf. Cic. Dom. 86; Diod. 14.117.5; Dion. Hal. 13.5; Plin. NH 34.13, Carvilius; Plut. Fort. Rom. 12, 324E-F; Flor. 1.22.4; App. Ital. 8; Dio fr. 24; Eutrop. 1.20; Auct. Vir Ill. 23, with the cognomen Saturninus; Zon. 7.22)." ;
